| Element | Mô tả |
|---|---|
| **[SCENE]** | Historical immersion — time, place, sensory detail |
| **[EVIDENCE]** | Data + authority citations (2-3/chapter) |
| **[MAINSTREAM]** | Official theory, presented fairly |
| **[COUNTER]** | Sharp pivot + counter-evidence |
| **[MYSTERY]** | 3-5 rhetorical questions, never resolved |

4 patterns (A-D), 15 universal rules, bao gồm:
- Pivot/Scene/Question variety (anti-repetition)
- Geographic transitions
- Callback closing
- Never resolve

